Description_lang: The cooldown of Coordinated Assault is reduced by ${$s1/-1000} sec and Coordinated Assault now grants $s2 stacks of Tip of the Spear.

description_blz.en_US: The cooldown of Coordinated Assault is reduced by 60 sec and Coordinated Assault now grants 3 stacks of Tip of the Spear.

description_blz.en_GB: The cooldown of Coordinated Assault is reduced by 60 sec and Coordinated Assault now grants 3 stacks of Tip of the Spear.

description_blz.ko_KR: 협공의 재사용 대기시간이 60초만큼 감소합니다. 또한 협공 사용 시 창끝 3중첩이 부여됩니다.
